{"tid":2456078,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：會免費向中小學派發國情讀本《我的家在中國》","createTime":"2021-03-21T15:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T02:52:14.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"630e9a37c4160bfe68dad3d74f6d0ce1daa82250","tid":2456078,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄接受內地中新社訪問表示，將會免費向全港中小學派發國情讀本《我的家在中國》，作為教輔材料。讀本在內地發行，有繁體版本，涵蓋6個範疇，包括城市、道路、山河等一共48本書。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄表示，會透過課程及不同科目，包括中文，中國歷史或地理科，傳揚重要價值觀，亦會透過《憲法》、《基本法》及國家安全教育的教材，輔助教學，當局會改善學校課程、提供教材指引、開展課外活動等，培養學生的國家觀念和身份認同，他認為國家過去經歷很多困難，需要一代又一代的愛國人士努力，才能令國家興盛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581761-20210321.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581761-20210321.htm&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbTaf%2B7McJKZiP%2F5rhSwlYLA%3D&h=c826b597\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581761-20210321.htm&h=0d72b778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581761-20210321.htm</a>"},{"pid":"29410d513c341e2319867f13afd153a1279add15","tid":2456078,"uid":76804,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"咁點解宜家仲唔比我番屋企?<br />\n我想番中國<br />\n點解仲封關唔比香港人去祖國食海底撈?"},{"pid":"1889977b2d62d74752132c7740e3ad996494f0ad","tid":2456078,"uid":46275,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:46:29.000Z","msg":"楊狗啲仔女個家喺邊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d5ed2393afbfc964740592cf1e9177639e4f1c","tid":2456078,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CMr1X8_Hwom/?igshid=2ybce53stgld\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMr1X8_Hwom%2F%3Figshid%3D2ybce53stgld&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbTaf%2B7McJKZ